{
  "texts": [
    "Fourth, we examined only a specific set of LLMs-namely, GPT-3.5 and GPT-4.",
    "Although these are extremely popular LLMs, many other LLMs exist and more are being created.",
    "For example, Alphabet (Google's parent company) just released Gemini, which was trained to be multimodal.",
    "Future LLMs may perform better on quantitative ability tests, but current state-of-the-art LLMs can already complete verbal ability tests comparably to humans with extremely high verbal ability.",
    "Overall, our results surface fresh concerns regarding the use of unproctored cognitive ability testing for pre-employment assessment."
  ]
}